			</form></div><div id="author_avatars-2" class="widget widget_author_avatars"><h3 class="widget-title">The Tribunal</h3><div class="author-list"><div class="user with-name name-group-0-j name-group-last-b user-1 with-biography bio-length- with-last-post" style=""><a href="https://www.sandwichtribunal.com/author/jim/" title="Jim Behymer (408 posts)"><span class="avatar"><img src='https://www.sandwichtribunal.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/SuperBeerGuy.jpg' srcset='https://www.sandwichtribunal.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/SuperBeerGuy.jpg 2x' class='avatar avatar-100 photo sab-custom-avatar' height='100' width='100' alt="avatar for Jim Behymer"  style=""  /></span><span class="name"><strong>Jim Behymer <span class="aa-post-count-wrap-start">(</span>408<span class="aa-post-count-wrap-end">)</span></strong></span></a><div class="biography"><p>I like sandwiches.</p>
